{"content": "I need to multiply 929 \u00d7 312 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 929 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 9\u00d711\u00b2 + 2\u00d711\u00b9 + 9\u00d711\u2070\n- 9\u00d7121 + 2\u00d711 + 9\u00d71\n- 1089 + 22 + 9\n- 1120\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 312 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- 3\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- 363 + 11 + 2\n- 376\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 1120 \u00d7 376 = 421,120\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 421,120 back to base 11**\n- 421120 \u00f7 11 = 38283 R 7\n- 38283 \u00f7 11 = 3480 R 3\n- 3480 \u00f7 11 = 316 R 4\n- 316 \u00f7 11 = 28 R 8\n- 28 \u00f7 11 = 2 R 6\n- 2 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 268437\n\n**Answer: 268437**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 372}